alomon smith barney holdings inc from  to  since  mr mundheim has also served as a professor of corporate law and finance at the university of arizona james e rogers college of law he was cochairman  of the new york law firm of fried frank harris shriver  jacobson llp and university professor of law and finance at the university of pennsylvania law school where he taught since  he was the university professor of law and finance at the university of pennsylvania from  to  and the dean of the university of pennsylvania law school from  to  in addition mr mundheim has served as general counsel of the us treasury department from  to  and as special counsel of the securities  exchange commission from  to  he served as chairman of the board of quadra realty trust inc since february  he serves as an independent director of a number of publicly held companies union capital corporation first pennsylvania bank corestates bank na  he has been an independent director of benjamin moore  co since  he has been an director at gogo inc since march   mr mundheim is a director at arnhold first eagle investment management llc and s bleichroeder advisers llc he has been director of cch incorporated commerce clearing house inc since  he also serves as a trustee and past president of the american academy in berlin a director and past president of the appleseed foundation and trustee of the new school university he is a member of the council of the american law institute and chairman of its governance committee mr mundheim is also the chairman of the legal advisory boards of nasdaq and the nasd he served as member of the supervisory board of hypo real estate holdings ag from june   to january   he was independent director of ecollegecom from january  to  he served as vice chairman governoratlarge and a member of the executive committee of the national association of securities dealers he serves as a trustee of the curtis institute of music he has served as a consultant to the american law 